column1: All right, so we'll have to start havin' the McCormicks make our meth again and-
How could you not have seen anything?? It's a whale, for Christ's sake!
Were you in there for three hours?!
A note? Let me see that.  We're taking Willzy-x home to the moon. Long live the zypods!  What the hell does that mean?
Don't let them get that whale in the water!
